summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 1589, for the improvement of Pasadena Place from East 49th Street to Northlake Avenue, all in the City of Seattle by grading and curbing the same, under Ordinance No. 16882 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against each parcel of land and part thereof shown in said roll, and providing for the collection thereof.
